# Enterprise Model Routing

This project uses multiple AI models.

No single model should be used for every task.

Always choose the model that provides the best balance between:

- Accuracy
- Reliability
- Speed
- Cost
- Context size
- Reasoning quality

Model routing is intentional.

Never choose a model randomly.

---

# Routing Principles

Always use the least expensive model capable of completing the task with the required quality.

Escalate only when necessary.

Never use the strongest model for simple work.

